                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Mission Section -->
                <section id="mission" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-matte-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-3 text-sm">1</span>
                        Our Mission
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash">
                        Our mission is to challenge the status quo by delivering transparent, customer-focused financial advice
                        and services. We believe in empowering our clients with knowledge and guiding them through every step of their journey.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Who We Are Section -->
                <section id="who-we-are" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-matte-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-3 text-sm">2</span>
                        Who We Are
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash mb-6">
                        We are a team of dedicated professionals passionate about helping individuals and families find the best financial solutions.
                        With a blend of expertise and innovation, we aim to make financial decisions simple, clear, and effective.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <img src="/images/team1.jpg" alt="Team 1" class="rounded-xl shadow-md object-cover w-full h-64" />
                        <img src="/images/team2.jpg" alt="Team 2" class="rounded-xl shadow-md object-cover w-full h-64" />
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- How We Help Section -->
                <section id="how-we-help" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-matte-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-3 text-sm">3</span>
                        How We Help
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash mb-6">
                        We support our clients through personalized advice, clear communication, and flexible solutions.
                        Whether you're buying your first home, investing, or looking to save, we provide step-by-step guidance.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash space-y-2">
                        <li>Tailored mortgage advice</li>
                        <li>Step-by-step financial guidance</li>
                        <li>Transparent and reliable communication</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <!-- Testimonials Section -->
                <section id="testimonials" class="scroll-mt-24">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-matte-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-3 text-sm">4</span>
                        Testimonials
                    </h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-matte-black rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                            <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash italic mb-4">"Fantastic service — they helped us every step of the way!"</p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white">Al Amin</h4>
                            <p class="text-yellow-500">★★★★★</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-matte-black rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                            <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash italic mb-4">"Professional, transparent, and highly supportive."</p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white">Jamil Jim</h4>
                            <p class="text-yellow-500">★★★★</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-matte-black rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                            <p class="text-matte-gray dark:text-light-ash italic mb-4">"Made complex financial decisions simple and stress-free."</p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-matte-black dark:text-white">Harique Jaif</h4>
                            <p class="text-yellow-500">★★★★★</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    // Smooth scrolling for anchor links
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
        anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');
            const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);

            if (targetElement) {
                window.scrollTo({
                    top: targetElement.offsetTop - 100,
                    behavior: 'smooth'
                });
            }
        });
    });
</script>
